    Package Description
    com.joliciel.talismane.parser
    Transition-based dependency parsing ( Parser) and output artefacts ( ParseConfiguration, ParseTree, and DependencyNode).
    com.joliciel.talismane.parser.features
    Various features specific to the dependency parsing phase.
    The available feature descriptors are listed in ParserFeatureParser.addFeatureClasses(com.joliciel.talismane.machineLearning.features.FeatureClassContainer)

    • Uses of Transition in com.joliciel.talismane.parser

      Classes in com.joliciel.talismane.parser that implement Transition 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AbstractTransition 
      class  ForceReduceTransition
      Special transition for ungoverned punctuation, so as not to consider it explicitly as depending on root, and not to create non-projectivity.
      class  LeftArcEagerTransition
      Create a dependency where Stack[0] depends on Buffer[0], and pop Stack[0].
      class  LeftArcTransition
      Create a dependency where Stack[0] depends on Buffer[0], and pop Stack[0].
      class  ReduceTransition
      Reduce the stack, by popping Stack[0], without creating a new dependency.
      class  RightArcEagerTransition
      Create a dependency where Buffer[0] depends on Stack[0], and push Buffer[0] to the top of the stack.
      class  RightArcTransition
      Create a dependency where Buffer[0] depends on Stack[0], remove Buffer[0], and put Stack[0] in its place.
      class  ShiftTransition
      Shift Buffer[0] over to Stack[0], without creating a new dependency.
